      "width": 830,
      "height": 40,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "V1 Section 6.1: On-device Whisper Tiny for voice-first interaction.\nProblem: 2-4s latency disorients elderly; degrades on regional dialects.",
