      "width": 840,
      "height": 40,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Hybrid decoding: sub-100ms streaming (10× faster); 22 scheduled languages.\nTimeline: G-02: 9-11 weeks (was 8-10, +2w Sherpa-ONNX eval).",
