      "height": 40,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "V1 Section 6.2, 9.1: Grade 6 readability for plain-language responses.\nCRITICAL FINDING: Mathematically invalid for agglutinative Indian languages.",
